Gekko Lydia Journal - #10 Lydia's last journal entry, written after the battle with a certain someone.

Gekko Jacket - #12 It’s Picky versus the cool kid in this long-awaited to show down. With his best friend on the line, Picky uses all the power at his disposal, even going so far as to use the look. Poor Scott.
Gekko Jacket - #13 Picky and Tracy ride off into the sunset while Scott gets what was probably coming to him for quite some time now.
Gekko Jacket - #14 The conclusion of this strange little side story.

Gekko Hallow - #01 Our heroes get a well deserved break and will be attending the annual Halloween party hosted at the Polestar Preschool. It seems like the gang is all here (including Ling), but where is Picky’s costume? And will Tracy’s car even make it to Twoson?
